## Style For Future Agents

When changing this repo:

- Prefer small, verifiable commits.
- Preserve user or remote uncommitted changes.
- Never reset or checkout away unknown edits.
- Use chronological splits only.
- Treat test set as sacred.
- Report trading usefulness metrics, not only generic ML scores.
- For Tokyo operations, use the private ignored doc and avoid printing secrets.
